'''數字推盤遊戲'''（n-puzzle）是一種最早的[[滑塊類遊戲|滑塊類遊戲]]，常見的類型有十五數字推盤遊戲和八數字推盤遊戲等。也有以圖畫代替數字的推盤遊戲。可能Noyes Palmer Chapman在1874年發明十五數字推盤<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cs.princeton.edu/courses/archive/spr09/cos226/assignments/8puzzle.html |title=COS 226 Programming Assignment 8 Puzzle |access-date=2010-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107214810/https://www.cs.princeton.edu/courses/archive/spr09/cos226/assignments/8puzzle.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但Sam Loyd則在1891年也宣稱為其發明<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cut-the-knot.org/pythagoras/fifteen.shtml |title=Sam Loyd's Fifteen |access-date=2010-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107214858/http://www.cut-the-knot.org/pythagoras/fifteen.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cut-the-knot.org/books/Reviews/The15Puzzle.shtml |title=The 15 Puzzle by Jerry Slocum and Dic Sonneveld  |access-date=2010-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107221311/http://www.cut-the-knot.org/books/Reviews/The15Puzzle.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

八數字推盤（又名'''重排九宮'''）則同樣是Noyes Palmer Chapman在1870年代發明<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gamescrafters.berkeley.edu/games.php?puzzle=8puzzle |title=8 puzzle |access-date=2010-11-11 |archive-date=2020-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908122350/http://gamescrafters.berkeley.edu/games.php?puzzle=8puzzle |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且[[馬丁·加德納|馬丁·加德納]]在[[科學人|科學人]]尋求更快的解答<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mathematische-basteleien.de/15puzzle.htm |title=The Eight Puzzle |access-date=2010-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107214901/http://www.mathematische-basteleien.de/15puzzle.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。也有人宣稱重排九宮是傳統中國遊戲，來自[[洛書|洛書]]，並且為[[華容道_(遊戲)|華容道]]的祖先<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cctv.com/program/kxlc/20030903/101220.shtml |title=橫刀立馬華容道 |access-date=2016-05-18 |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107214844/http://www.cctv.com/program/kxlc/20030903/101220.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

